{%- comment -%}
Honeypot autofill-clear. Externalized to /assets/js/form-handling.js (not inline) so the
Content-Security-Policy can keep a strict script-src 'self'. Loaded only on pages that render
the lead form. The JSON-LD in head.liquid is type="application/ld+json" (a data block, not
script-src governed), so the form pages' honeypot is the site's only executable script.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign siteData = site.data.global -%}
{%- if page.hasForm -%}
<script src="{{ siteData.basePath }}assets/js/form-handling.js" defer></script>
{%- endif -%}
